  "title": "SITE SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title:</strong> Site Supervisor (Civil & Structural)</p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Singapore (Project Sites)<br />\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br />\n<strong>Reporting To:</strong> Project Manager / Construction Manager</p><p><strong>Role Overview</strong></p><p>Lead day-to-day site execution for <strong>civil engineering\nworks</strong> including <strong>drainage construction</strong> and <strong>RC structures</strong>\n(retaining walls, bridge abutment walls). Drive safety, quality, and programme\ndelivery on the ground.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise\n     daily works: excavation, drainage, RC works, backfilling, reinstatement.</li><li>Coordinate\n     manpower/subcontractors, sequencing, and site logistics.</li><li>Ensure\n     drainage line/level/gradient accuracy and proper installation of\n     pipes/manholes.</li><li>Oversee\n     RC works: formwork, rebar, embedments, concreting, curing, and finishing.</li><li>Enforce\n     WSH requirements; conduct toolbox meetings and maintain site control.</li><li>Prepare\n     daily progress updates and site documentation; escalate risks early.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>3–7\n     years</strong> relevant experience in civil & structural works (drainage +\n     RC).</li><li>Able\n     to read drawings/specs and execute method statements effectively.</li><li>Strong\n     on-site coordination, leadership, and problem-solving.</li><li>Preferred:\n     <strong>BCSS/WSQ</strong> and relevant WSH training.</li></ul><p><strong>Compensation</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive\n     salary (commensurate with experience)</li><li>Incentives\n     (where applicable)</li><li>Performance-based\n     progression</li></ul><p><strong>Apply</strong></p><p>Email your CV (project experience, certifications,\navailability, expected salary, notice period) to <a href=\"mailto:careers@dongce.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">careers@dongce.com.sg</a>.</p>",
